is applicable for the following states: arunachal pradesh – permits are issued by the secretary of the government of arunachal pradesh. the permits are required for entering the indian state of arunachal pradesh through any of the check gates across the inter-state border with assam or nagaland. mizoram – permits are issued by the government of mizoram. the permit is required for entering the indian state of mizoram through any of the check gates across the inter-state borders. nagaland – a permit is mandatory for a mainland indian citizen entering the state of nagaland through any of the check gates 